To be exact – 2 servings in every 11.5 ounce can of this delicious vegetable juice is made with no sugar added and no artificial colors. Taste the unquestionable goodness of this plant-based drink made made with tomatoes, carrots and a blend of celery, beets, parsley, lettuce, watercress and spinach. Take V8 vegetable juice on the go as a veggie snack – it's full of feel-good nutrients your body needs like antioxidant vitamins. V8 100% Vegetable Juice is a delicious veggie snack for any time of day and can even help curb those late night cravings! Drinking V8 Vegetable Juice is a super convenient and lower calorie option than a sugary juice. Not to mention, adding vegetables to your day is an important part of any diet. V8=Vegetables=Good. V8 Juice was born out of the idea that great taste and great nutrition can go hand in hand. For over 8 decades, that idea has thrived. Because getting the veggies you need in the drink you love fuels a day well lived. V8. There's nothing like the original. Trusted since 1933.
